{"tid":1212340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝擊立法會：消息指4萬人參與暴動　政府堅持不撤不押後","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:01:03.000Z","uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c530e640af369afafb746e45b133911a9a1617cf","tid":1212340,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"0026 夏慤道大量示威者散去<br />\n大批示威者周三(12日)佔據立法會一帶主要幹道反對《逃犯條例》修訂，爆發連場衝突，警方將示威定性為暴動。政府消息稱，有4萬人參與暴動，遠遠超過針對一條修例的評估示威人數，因而認為周三示威是一場有組織暴動，有人欲藉年輕人在香港發動顏色革命，營造政府無法管治亂象。不過，消息稱，政府對修訂《逃犯條例》抱堅持態度，不會撤回法案，也不會押後二讀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/jr1Z82?utm_source=washare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2Fjr1Z82%3Futm_source%3Dwashare&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=02a2a995\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/jr1Z82?utm_source=washare</a>"},{"pid":"8d920bb88a7725a91551475d85cf75aa87da4133","tid":1212340,"uid":78573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"屋企大把野可以當盾用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4f08a5a341d6f6632e9c534c66da5ca412249e","tid":1212340,"uid":75610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"遠遠超過針對一條修例的評估示威人數，因而認為周三示威是一場有組織暴動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁撚厚面皮唔覺得自己有問題"},{"pid":"c350c335909ee43d53893b90d767770ad13a7093","tid":1212340,"uid":18739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:47:08.000Z","msg":"林鄭政府淆緊底，唔肯承認自己無能力管治香港，唯有屈落其他人度，希望可以卸膊過骨"},{"pid":"bd5cb579f050ee0067d26341fd0f6beeb5280ef2","tid":1212340,"u